{"tid":1760493,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"End Game 係一場大仗, 唔係只得一下,大家要加油","createTime":"2019-11-28T08:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T16:10:12.000Z","uid":85751,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d94268daad2b56a6e71176132a030e3bb01c32c1","tid":1760493,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"而家情況就係開哂好多 portal 好多人黎幫手 (eg. 外國, 香港區選)<br />\nDr Strange 話得一個機會, 一個機會就係回應五大訴求<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPYKa1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPYKa1d.jpg&h=abfdc2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvels ( 香港人) vs Thanos (中共)<br />\n大家都係爭緊隻 Infinity gloves , gloves 上有 6粒石 (而其實都加至六大訴求: 解散警隊)<br />\n<br />\n邊個有隻手套, 啪到手指, 解決訴求, 世界先會會復正常 (post-end game spider-man)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0b3qEUD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0b3qEUD.png&h=5cc0fa6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以,而家仲係打緊仗, 大家角力緊, 唔好鬆懈, 繼續日程表<br />\n做大黃色經濟圈, 杯葛一切藍, 中資<br />\n星星之火, 可以燎原, 燒埋上支那, 先係打大仗<br />\n攰可以休息, 但團火一定唔可以熄<br />\n<br />\n光復香港, 時代革命"},{"pid":"4e822f1bce928ef8213a386384a5108220ecc985","tid":1760493,"uid":44428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"幫手推行動po!!!<br />\n[今晚愛丁堡美國旗海!!!]<br />\n全世界同我入嚟 save美國國旗落電話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1760489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1760489</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>有旗帶旗, 冇旗print旗, print唔到就用電話show出嚟<br />\n要全場都係美國旗!!!</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvZ9mYV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvZ9mYV.jpg&h=361452eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEFwAcN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEFwAcN.png&h=a0392b7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HddumSO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHddumSO.gif&h=bb9ce76b&